{"tid":2452671,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬：輸波係球員態度出問題","createTime":"2021-03-19T03:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T03:23:14.000Z","uid":78243,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bc12acd0842c4c4933561823b5a03c1d3041a842","tid":2452671,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】熱刺在歐霸盃大好形勢下出局，領隊摩連奴坦言感覺比傷心更甚，並對球員態度有微言。<br />\n「我的球隊，我重申，是我的球隊，球員不像參與一場重要的比賽，或許當中有人認為並不重要，我覺的重要。」歐霸盃16強次回合，首回合領先2:0的熱刺全場受壓，更被薩格勒布戴拿模射手奧斯錫大演帽子戲法，結果反輸2:3，爆冷出局，領隊摩連奴賽後埋怨球員比賽態度差。<br />\n<br />\n他續說：「說我悲傷並不足夠，我感覺比悲傷更甚。足球的本質是態度，人家藉此打敗我們，我告誡球員以此態度比賽有多危險，而這發生了，因為我相信球員直到對方攻入第2球才感到凶險。」他還罕有地到敵方更衣室慈賀對手。<br />\n<br />\n繼在北倫敦打吡戰敗陣，以至在歐霸盃出局，摩佬的帥位難免受動搖，下月與曼城爭奪英聯盃，對他而言是不容有失。<br />\n<br />\nNow 體育 - <a href=\"http://sports.now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=174489ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">sports.now.com</a><br />\n<br />\n迷摩：摩佬好偉大，故意罵球證將球員既壓力轉嫁俾自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca96e0687ebae7f7a2fd584a30ca74f63700cf31","tid":2452671,"uid":294,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5SKh6So.gif&amp;h=2b461dae&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"9732521585197c994e15cbeb4b93f5cf143dce9f","tid":2452671,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f76fce7aa1f56303259e49bedc03c41adcef6e","tid":2452671,"uid":47641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:17:00.000Z","msg":"摩佬：比悲傷更悲傷的故事"},{"pid":"e65bcc600b49560e330e4cf867427bdb288